      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Some vesk learn to watch their environment and other creatures around them for signs of danger. Vesk with this racial trait select either @Compendium[sfrpg.skills.CzEAY60hUMyfOC4G]{Perception} or @Compendium[sfrpg.skills.wZkmlFdp7B8md8FO]{Sense Motive}. They gain a +3 racial bonus to checks with the chosen skill. Once this choice is made, it cannot be changed.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces fearless.</strong></p>\n<p><strong><br /></strong><em>Edit the modifier in the Modifiers tab to the chosen skill.</em></p>"
